---
title: Italian Chicken Salad & Bacon Croutons with Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: How to improve golden, aromatic croutons? Just add bacon, of course! Sprinkle them over a hearty salad of succulent chicken, crisp greens and a creamy pesto dressing to make a fresh-tasting feast that'll be loved by all.
